Output demo.gif

Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 880
Set Height 520
Set Padding 16
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set CursorBlink false

# Title
Type "# flyto-core: give your AI 412 tools"
Enter
Sleep 400ms

# Install
Type "pip install flyto-core[browser]"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Type@1ms "Successfully installed flyto-core-2.12.12"
Enter
Sleep 600ms

# Run demo
Type "python demo.py"
Enter
Sleep 300ms

# Simulated output
Type@1ms ""
Enter
Type@1ms "flyto-core demo -- 412 tools for AI agents"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Type@1ms ""
Enter
Type@1ms "--- Step 1: browser.launch ---"
Enter
Sleep 400ms
Type@1ms "[ok] Browser launched (headless)"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Type@1ms ""
Enter
Type@1ms "--- Step 2: browser.goto ---"
Enter
Sleep 400ms
Type@1ms "[ok] Navigated to Hacker News"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Type@1ms ""
Enter
Type@1ms "--- Step 3: browser.extract ---"
Enter
Sleep 400ms
Type@1ms "[ok] Extracted top 5 stories:"
Enter
Sleep 100ms
Type@1ms ""
Enter
Type@1ms "  1. Gemini 3.1 Pro"
Enter
Sleep 80ms
Type@1ms "  2. Show HN: Micasa - track your house from the terminal"
Enter
Sleep 80ms
Type@1ms "  3. Micropayments as a reality check for news sites"
Enter
Sleep 80ms
Type@1ms "  4. A terminal weather app with ASCII animations"
Enter
Sleep 80ms
Type@1ms "  5. Why SQLite is perfect for edge computing"
Enter
Sleep 400ms
Type@1ms ""
Enter
Type@1ms "--- Step 4: string.uppercase ---"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Type@1ms "[ok] FLYTO-CORE: 412 TOOLS, ZERO CONFIG"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Type@1ms ""
Enter
Type@1ms "--- Step 5: browser.close ---"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Type@1ms "[ok] Browser closed"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Type@1ms ""
Enter
Type@1ms "Done! 5 tools executed. No LLM calls. Deterministic."
Enter

Sleep 3s
